rder-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;\"><b>山海迎新第三式：第二届AIO新春庙会</b></h1><h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;\"><b>时间：春节期间</b></h1><h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;\"><b>地点：黑森林酒店</b></h1><h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;\"><b>主题：美食荟萃、欢乐互动</b></h1><h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;\"><b>&nbsp; &nbsp;春节期间，黑森林酒店将举办第二届“AIO新春庙会”，充满着新春元素的装饰、装扮席卷整个景区。“年味儿”十足的新春庙会将集合互动游戏、趣味体验、特色小吃三大传统庙会活动于一体，让游客感受来自东部华侨城的独特“年味儿”，还有感染力互动性极强的变装表演，琳琅满目的特色工艺将在现场精彩呈现，展现中华传统民俗的惊艳魅力。</b></h1><h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;\"><img src=\"/hqc_mp/upload/articleImg/201706/1497434624372u=3163461808,704686000&amp;fm=23&amp;gp=0.jpg\" data-filename=\"img\" style=\"width: 100%;\"><br></h1><h1 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px; border-image-source: initial; border-image-slice: initial; border-image-width: initial; border-image-outset: initial; border-image-repeat: initial; margin: 20px 0px 10px; padding: 0px;\"><b>山海迎新第四式：大华兴寺新春祈福</b></