(5,'天禅门票','upload/goodsThumb/201706/1496393534626QQ截图20170602092519.png',NULL,21,2,1995728000,91,100.00,100.00,4500,'<span style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">【景点名称】：深圳东部华侨城《天禅》表演<br style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word;\">【门票种类】：电子票，无需快递。</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px;\">现场兑换门票。<br style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word;\"></span>【有效日期】：需按指定日期使用。<br style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word;\">【表演时间】：每天下午16:00-17:00</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\">。</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px;\">（仅供参考,请以园区当天公告为准)<br style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word;\">【演出地点】：深圳东部华侨城大剧院（剧场位于茶溪谷园区内，请自行额外购买茶溪谷门票。）<br style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word;\"></span>【换票须知】：</span><span style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(136, 136, 136); font-family: 宋体, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25px;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; font-size: 14px;\">预订成功后将会以短信的形式将“取票凭证码”发送到下单时指定的手机。客人凭订单号、短信以及有效证件在<strong style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">深圳东部华侨城咨询中心</span></strong>驴妈妈验证机上打印凭证。由工作人员在凭证上盖章确认已付款。持凭证前往相应的地点获取对应的票据。请于园区关门前一个小时兑换完毕。</span><br style=\"word-break: break-all; word-wrap: break-word;\">【门市价格】：价格：普通席￥100/人，贵宾席￥150人</span>','<div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Simsun; line-height: 21px;\"><span style=\"word-wrap: break-word; font-weight: 700;\">兑换要求</span></div><div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 17.1429px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">积分数量充足并且您的积分满足相应商品兑换要求，即可参与兑换。</span></div><div style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 17.1429px;\"><font color=\"#444444\" face=\"Tahoma, Microsoft Yahei, Simsun\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px;\"><br></span></font></div><div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Simsun; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"></font></font></div><div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Simsun; line-height: 21px;\"><div><span style=\"font-weight: 700; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">兑换方法</span></div><font face=\"微软雅黑\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\">提交兑换申请后，系统即扣取相应积分。</font></div><div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 12px; line-height: 17.1429px; word-wrap: break-word;\"><div><font color=\"#444444\"><span style=\"line-height: 21px;\"><br></span></font></div><font color=\"#444444\" face=\"Tahoma, Microsoft Yahei, Simsun\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><div style=\"line-height: 21px;\"><br></div></font></div><div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, \'Microsoft Yahei\', Simsun; line-height: 21px;\"><font face=\"微软雅黑\" style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"><font style=\"word-wrap: break-word;\"></font></font></div><div align=\"left\" style=\"font-size: 14px; word-wrap: break-word; colo